Method Detail

getTargetPage

Identifiable getTargetPage()
Returns the target page associated with this wire. If null is returned, this implies that an in page wire is to be created. The page represented by the LayoutModelController which provided the WireModelController intended for creating the wire will be used as target page for the wire to be created. For creating a cross page wire, the return value of this method mustnÂ´t be null.

Returns:
The target page Identifiable, or null.
